description: This top 5% Parvati purrs with a rating of 70, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 210, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Nine Lives for East, 3 for South, and 1 for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [210 Votes, Top 5%]
